Description
IMGTransfer is a versatile application designed to streamline the process of image handling, compression, and conversion. With support for a wide range of formats and intuitive features, IMGTransfer enables users to easily manage and manipulate images for various purposes, including generating QR codes, converting between image formats, and exporting to SVG or PDF.
Key Features:
Image compression to JPEG and PNG with adjustable quality. Resizing images and exporting them in SVG format. Conversion of JPG images to PDF and PDF pages to JPG. QR code generation and export in SVG and PNG formats. User-friendly interface with drag-and-drop support.
Acknowledgments:
Special thanks to the open-source community for providing the tools and libraries that made this application possible.
